Core:
 - Pins can be specified also by source package.
 - Correctness of APT options is checked.

Searching:
 - 'search' command searches all versions of package, not policy or
   default ones;
 - 'search' command can search case-sensitively ('--case-sensitive' switch);

Show:
 - 'show' command can show release description ('--with-release-info' switch);
 - '/<distribution' and '=<version>' suffixes can be used with 'depends' and
   'rdepends' commands.

Managing packages:
 - 'safe-upgrade' and 'full-upgrade' commands can accept additional packages
   (with optional modifiers) from the command line;
 - 'satisfy' command is present.
 - passes '--force-*' options to dpkg only when really needed, not always
